Package com.cmas.model

Class CampCommMember

java.lang.Object
com.cmas.model.User
com.cmas.model.Student
com.cmas.model.CampCommMember
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CampCommMember extends Student
Model class representing a camp committee member, extending the functionality of the Student class. It includes additional attributes and methods specific to camp committee members. The class maintains information about the camp suggestions provided by the committee member, the camp ID associated with their committee role, and a points system to track their contributions.
Since:
2023-11-18
